gov.nasa.gsfc.hessi.jidl.prep.server.Parameter
Class PrepParameter

java.lang.Object
  gov.nasa.gsfc.hessi.jidl.prep.server.Parameter.PrepParameter

public class PrepParameter
extends java.lang.Object

This class is the entity that holds pairs of parameters and values. Each PrepParameter has a parameter name and value which will be used directly in Preprocessor.preprocess()

Since:
Revision 19

Field Detail

name

private java.lang.String name
The name of the parameter. Has to be the real name used by the preprocessing routine for the given instrument

value

private java.lang.Object[] value
This member holds the value assigned to this parameter. Even if it is a single value, to stay flexible and being able to deal with arrays, it is always an array.
